# Reserved for repository pattern (data access layer).
#
# Architecture rule #10: "Keep repository interfaces so D1 can migrate later."
# Each repository should:
#   - Export an interface (e.g., PatientRepository)
#   - Export a D1 implementation (e.g., createPatientRepository(db))
#   - Return plain entity types from src/shared/types
#   - Never accept or return D1-specific types like D1Result outside this layer
#
# Suggested modules (Phase 2+):
# - tenants.ts
# - branches.ts
# - users.ts
# - patients.ts
# - visits.ts
# - findings.ts
# - treatment-plans.ts
# - payments.ts
# - files.ts
# - audit-logs.ts
# - lark-sync-logs.ts